Types of Secrets\
 - Opaque/Generic		-	the data is unstructured, just some key value pairs as text, arbitary\
 - Service Account Token	-	authentication token for a service account\
 - dockercfg			-	image pull secret\
 - dockerconfigjson		-	image pull secret\
 - basic-auth			-	credentials for basic authentication\
 - ssh-auth			-	credentials for ssh authentication\
 - tls				-	public certificate and private key\
 - token			-	kubernetes.io/service-account-token (service account token)\
					bootstrap.kubernetes.io/token (bootstrap token data)\
